sequenceDiagram
    participant FE as Frontend
    participant Cmd as ai.rs
    participant Ctx as context.rs
    participant Red as RedactionEngine
    participant API as claude_api.rs
    participant Claude as api.anthropic.com

    FE->>Cmd: invoke("ai_translate_command", {query, context})
    Cmd->>Cmd: Generate request_id (UUID)
    Cmd-->>FE: { request_id } (immediate return)

    Note over Cmd,Claude: Async task spawned
    Cmd->>Ctx: build_system_prompt(context, redaction)
    Ctx->>Red: redact(recent_commands)
    Red-->>Ctx: sanitized context
    Ctx-->>Cmd: system prompt string

    Cmd->>API: send_message_streaming(key, model, prompt, messages, callback)
    API->>Claude: POST /v1/messages (stream: true)
    Claude-->>API: SSE: message_start
    API->>API: Extract model name, input_tokens

    loop For each SSE chunk
        Claude-->>API: SSE: content_block_delta
        API->>Cmd: callback(TextDelta(text))
        Cmd->>FE: emit("ai:stream-chunk", {rid, text})
    end

    Claude-->>API: SSE: message_delta (stop_reason, output_tokens)
    API->>Cmd: callback(Completion(metadata))
    Cmd->>FE: emit("ai:stream-end", {rid, model, tokens})
